body_html:
I had the same issue ( AttributeError: '_NamespacePath' object has no attribute 'sort' ) with TF v1.9.0-rc2 and v1.8.0; on Ubuntu 16.04, Python 3.5.2, protobuf 3.6.

Fixed it by downgrading protobuff to 3.5.1.
